Package: a5view
Title: Interactive Map Viewer for A5 Geospatial Cells
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hugh", "Graham", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hugh@belian.earth"),
    person("belian.earth", role = "cph")
    )
Description: An 'htmlwidgets' viewer that renders 'A5' geospatial index
    cells on an interactive map using 'deck.gl'. Supports colour mapping,
    palette selection, basemap switching, opacity control, tooltips and cell
    borders (among other features).
